## ğŸ’¡ Why This Structure is Better

Based on research from:
- âœ… **Plex/Jellyfin**: "One folder per item, all files together"
- âœ… **yt-dlp experts**: Organize by category and title
- âœ… **Professional archivists**: Keep metadata with media files
- âœ… **Content creators**: Category + date organization

**This is the industry standard.** Used by professionals worldwide.

