## ğŸš¨ Quick Troubleshooting

### Script won't run?
```bash
chmod +x download.sh
```

### yt-dlp not found?
```bash
python3 -m pip install -U yt-dlp
```

### Wrong category?
Just move the folder:
```bash
mv Music/2026-01-13-Video/ Podcasts/
```

